## 10. Scope Boundary: relurpish

`app/relurpish/` (TUI, runtime adapter, session export) is a **consumer** of the
framework and is treated as a separate concern from this spec. Changes required
in relurpish to make use of framework features (e.g. `RegisterTaskGrant`, Nexus
WS client, `SQLiteEventLog`) are noted in the roadmap as integration points but
their internal implementation is outside this document's scope.

